        self.client.get("/data", headers=headers, params={"ip": "192.168.1.2"})
```

### Conclusion

By implementing dynamic rate limiting, whitelisting trusted IPs or users, and thorough testing, you can ensure that your rate limiting setup is effective at mitigating DDoS attacks and other abuses while minimizing false positives.

